<item>
            <title>[LU-415] sanityn test_4: Mtimes don&apos;t match 1308053256, 1308068405</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-415</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sanityn test 4 failed as follows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== test 4: fstat validation on multiple mount points ========== == 05:07:34
Mtimes don&apos;t match 1308053256, 1308068405
 sanityn test_4: @@@@@@ FAIL: test_4 failed with 1
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Maloo report: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/7209239a-96f3-11e0-9a27-52540025f9af&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/7209239a-96f3-11e0-9a27-52540025f9af&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is caused by the mismatched clocks between the client and server nodes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;$ pdsh -l root -S -w client-[10,12],fat-amd-[1-2] date
client-10: Tue Jun 14 12:43:33 PDT 2011
client-12: Tue Jun 14 12:43:44 PDT 2011
fat-amd-1: Tue Jun 14 19:43:29 PDT 2011
fat-amd-2: Tue Jun 14 19:43:28 PDT 2011
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;However, per the comments from Andreas in &lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=18169&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;bug 18169&lt;/a&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This &lt;em&gt;should&lt;/em&gt; work correctly so should be investigated, but isn&apos;t a release blocking problem.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;br/&gt;
Lustre Branch: v1_8_6_RC2&lt;br/&gt;
Lustre Build: &lt;a href=&quot;http://newbuild.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b1_8/80/&quot;&gt;http://newbuild.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b1_8/80/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
e2fsprogs Build: &lt;a href=&quot;http://newbuild.whamcloud.com/job/e2fsprogs-master/40/&quot;&gt;http://newbuild.whamcloud.com/job/e2fsprogs-master/40/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Distro/Arch: RHEL6/x86_64(patchless client, in-kernel OFED, kernel version: 2.6.32-131.2.1.el6)&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;RHEL5/x86_64(server, OFED 1.5.3.1, kernel version: 2.6.18-238.12.1.el5_lustre)&lt;br/&gt;
</environment>
